    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. Smith,",
        "I am writing to request for twenty days' leave in the next month. In order to have backup resource for a smooth execution of work in my absence, I wanted to have an prior approval.",
        "As you are aware that I have a younger sister in my siblings, I am glad to share that her marriage has been finalized and scheduled in the month of August. It is going to be grand ceremony in my home country for which my presence will be required there because in India, it is considered a bad omen to not have the brother present in their sister's wedding.",
        "At the least, I will be requiring 20 days off from work as I will be the one responsible for all the prepartions during this event. Moreover, I have to stay back for few days after concluding the function so as to see off all the guests. My responsibilities are even more significant as there is no one else to complete our religious rituals.",
        "While I will be in India, I would be available online for any critical situation. However, I have planned handover my task to my teammate Mr. Kumar for routine day to day activities. Also, I will ensure to finish off all my pendencies before the period of my absence.",
        "The invitation for the occasion will reach you in coming few days and I would really appreatiate your visit in my sister's wedding.",
        "Yours sincerely,",
        "Aman Malik"
    ],
